    "class": "name"
   },
   "html": "\n[ まさき・じんざぶろう ]"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n陸軍教育総監、参謀次長、台湾軍司令官、第１師団長、陸軍士官学校校長、陸軍大将"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "lt"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"07m.html\">一覧　（マ）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/redirect?link_code=ur2&amp;tag=click20thcetu-22&amp;camp=247&amp;creative=1211&amp;path=external-search%3Fsearch-type=ss%26index=blended%26keyword=%25E7%259C%259F%25E5%25B4%258E%2520%25E7%2594%259A%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%2583%258E\" target=\"_blank\">本を入手</a><img src=\"http://www.assoc-amazon.jp/e/ir?t=click20thcetu-22&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=9\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\"></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　佐賀県出身。陸士卒。日露戦争に従軍。陸大卒。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　陸士校長時代、尊皇絶対主義の訓育に努め、安藤輝三、<a href=\"../p/iasaici.html\">磯部浅一</a>らを輩出。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　台湾軍司令官など経て参謀次長に就任、<a href=\"../p/asadao.html\">荒木陸相</a>とともに皇道派を形成。勢力伸張を図る。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　ついで教育総監に就任、<a href=\"../1935/02kikan.html\">天皇機関説問題</a>では国体明徴運動を積極的に推進。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../p/hsenjuro.html\">林陸相</a>による反皇道派人事により<a href=\"../1935/07masak.html\">罷免され</a>、これが<a href=\"../1935/08aizaw.html\">相沢事件</a>、<a href=\"../1936/02226ji.html\">二・二六事件</a>の誘因となる。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../1936/02226ji.html\">二・二六事件</a>では、安藤、<a href=\"../p/iasaici.html\">磯部</a>らに共感を示しつつ、収拾に努める。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../1936/02226ji.html\">事件</a>後、「反乱幇助」の容疑で軍法会議にかけられるも無罪。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　戦後、戦犯として逮捕されるが不起訴。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
